# Troubleshooting
# ============================================
# If you get PERMISSION_DENIED errors:
# 1. Verify you're using the correct account: gcloud auth list
# 2. Switch account if needed: gcloud config set account YOUR_EMAIL
# 3. Re-authenticate: gcloud auth application-default login
# 4. Ensure Vertex AI API is enabled in your project
